sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Nuclei were isolated with Nuclei EZ Lysis buffer (NUC-101; Sigma-Aldrich) supplemented with protease inhibitor (5892791001; Roche). Samples were cut into < 2 mm pieces, homogenized using a Dounce homogenizer (885302–0002; Kimble Chase) in 2 ml of ice-cold Nuclei EZ Lysis buffer, and incubated on ice for 5 minutes with an additional 2 ml of lysis buffer.
